\cos x \approx 1 - \frac{x^2}{2},
\frac{1-\cos x}{1-\cos \frac{x}{1+x}} \approx (1+x)^2.
\approx \frac{(1+x)^{2z}-1}{x} \approx \frac{(1+2zx)-1}{x} = 2z.
{\displaystyle \lim_{x \rightarrow 0} {1 - \cos(x) \over x^2} = {1 \over 2}}
